---
---
<section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full max-w-7xl pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 text-green-400 text-xs font-medium mb-6">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
        </span>
        Clientes Satisfechos
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Resultados <span class="text-green-500">Reales</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Empresas peruanas que ya están vendiendo en piloto automático.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="group p-1 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-transparent hover:from-green-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="bg-[#0F1110] p-8 rounded-xl h-full relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-white"><path d="M14.017 21L14.017 18C14.017 16.8954 13.1216 16 12.017 16H9L9.00001 21H14.017ZM14.017 14L14.017 6.00002L9.00001 6.00002L9 14H14.017ZM4.00001 21L4.00001 18C4.00001 16.8954 4.89544 16 6.00001 16H8.00001L8.00001 21H4.00001ZM8.00001 14L8.00001 6.00002L4.00001 6.00002L4.00001 14H8.00001ZM20.017 21L20.017 18C20.017 16.8954 19.1216 16 18.017 16H16L16 21H20.017ZM20.017 14L20.017 6.00002L16 6.00002L16 14H20.017Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-500 mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            "Antes perdía ventas por no responder rápido. Ahora el bot atiende a todos mis clientes al instante y solo me pasa los que están listos para pagar. ¡Increíble!"
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-white/5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-indigo-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              CM
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Carlos M.</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Tienda de Ropa</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="group p-1 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-transparent hover:from-green-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="bg-[#0F1110] p-8 rounded-xl h-full relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-white"><path d="M14.017 21L14.017 18C14.017 16.8954 13.1216 16 12.017 16H9L9.00001 21H14.017ZM14.017 14L14.017 6.00002L9.00001 6.00002L9 14H14.017ZM4.00001 21L4.00001 18C4.00001 16.8954 4.89544 16 6.00001 16H8.00001L8.00001 21H4.00001ZM8.00001 14L8.00001 6.00002L4.00001 6.00002L4.00001 14H8.00001ZM20.017 21L20.017 18C20.017 16.8954 19.1216 16 18.017 16H16L16 21H20.017ZM20.017 14L20.017 6.00002L16 6.00002L16 14H20.017Z"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-500 mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            "Mis pacientes ahora agendan sus citas solos por WhatsApp. Me ahorra horas de estar pegada al teléfono confirmando horarios. 100% recomendado."
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-white/5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500 to-rose-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              AS
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Ana S.</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Clínica Dental</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="group p-1 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-transparent hover:from-green-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="bg-[#0F1110] p-8 rounded-xl h-full relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-white"><path d="M14.017 21L14.017 18C14.017 16.8954 13.1216 16 12.017 16H9L9.00001 21H14.017ZM14.017 14L14.017 6.00002L9.00001 6.00002L9 14H14.017ZM4.00001 21L4.00001 18C4.00001 16.8954 4.89544 16 6.00001 16H8.00001L8.00001 21H4.00001ZM8.00001 14L8.00001 6.00002L4.00001 6.00002L4.00001 14H8.00001ZM20.017 21L20.017 18C20.017 16.8954 19.1216 16 18.017 16H16L16 21H20.017ZM20.017 14L20.017 6.00002L16 6.00002L16 14H20.017Z"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-yellow-500 mb-6">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            "La mejor inversión para mi negocio. El menú automático es muy fácil de usar y mis clientes están felices con la rapidez de la atención."
          </p>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-6 border-t border-white/5">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              JL
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Jorge L.</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>